you to own the stock.
But you might prefer money: Perhaps your startup has been private for a lon=
g time, its valuation is high, you=E2=80=99d like a new house, and you=E2=
=80=99d like to cash out a bit now. Often, these days, mature private=C2=A0=
tech startups recognize this problem and periodically buy back stock from e=
