sirable. She can=C2=A0sell=C2=A0it, too. If she no longer likes the company=
, or if the company=E2=80=99s valuation has gone up and she wants to take p=
rofits, there=E2=80=99s probably some other investor=C2=A0who wants exposur=
e to a hot startup and who will pay her $60 or whatever for that forward. M=
