ccc;">put out a statement</a> about that one too:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CAs we=E2=80=99ve said all=
 along, there was nothing novel about this matter, and the jury agreed: thi=
s was insider trading, pure and simple. Defendant [Matthew Panuwat]=C2=A0us=
ed highly confidential information about an impending announcement of the a=
cquisition of biopharmaceutical company Medivation, Inc., the company where=
 he worked, by Pfizer Inc. to trade ahead of the news for his own enrichmen=
t. Rather than buying the securities of Medivation, however, Panuwat used h=
is employer=E2=80=99s confidential information to acquire a large stake in =
call options of another comparable public company, Incyte Corporation, whos=
