on: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000=
; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">examples</a>.) There=
 is some baseline level of risk that you have to take as a trader to=C2=A0<=
em>avoid=C2=A0</em>getting fired, and perhaps if getting fired is cushy eno=
ugh your reaction will be laziness rather than risk-taking.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/34967840.259352/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZ=
XdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDQtMDUvaGVkZ2UtZnVuZC1oZWFkaHVudGVyLXNheXMtdG9wLXRh=
