toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">here =
is a claim that</a> =E2=80=9Cthe hedge fund industry=E2=80=99s biggest star=
s are looking beyond money when they plot their career moves, according to =
IDW Group founder and Chief Executive Officer Ilana Weinstein=E2=80=9D:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">After a year or two of guaranteed compensation=
 in a new role, =E2=80=9Cyou=E2=80=99re out and you=E2=80=99re on your own,=
 so to speak, and you need to put up the goods,=E2=80=9D Weinstein said Fri=
day in a Bloomberg Television interview. =E2=80=9CThe question becomes: Are=
 you really set up for success, how do you develop, and what are the resour=
ces the firm has to get you there?=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9C=E2=80=98Will I be better by virtue o=
f making this move, developmentally =E2=80=94 will I be the best version of=
 myself?=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D she said. =E2=80=9CThe second question is, =E2=
=80=98Is there more opportunity at this place that I=E2=80=99m going to, re=
lative to where I=E2=80=99m at?=E2=80=99=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I feel like I=E2=80=99d probably be a better v=
ersion with myself with=C2=A0more money.</p>
